OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FIt has been almost nine years since
OL,8,Fone of Brazil's worst environmental
OL,9,Fdisasters.
OL,11,FToday, the case against a British
OL,12,Fmining company, which many hold
OL,13,Fresponsible, began. It has become the
OL,14,Flargest class action in English legal
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,FIn 2015, 19 people were swept to their
OL,18,Fdeaths; in a matter of minutes.
