OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe village of Bento Rodrigues in
OL,8,FBrazil was wiped out as 44.5 million
OL,9,Fcubic metres of mining waste was
OL,10,Freleased following the Fundao Dam
OL,11,Fcollapse.
OL,13,FIt also had a devastating
OL,14,Fenvironmental impact. Mining sludge
OL,15,Ftravelled 675 kilometres, reaching the
OL,16,FAtlantic Ocean. 11 tonnes of fish were
OL,17,Fkilled and 860 hectares of Atlantic
OL,18,FForest were degraded.
