OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FToday, some of those who lost loved
OL,8,Fones and livelihoods in the disaster
OL,9,Fhave come face to face with those they
OL,10,Fhold responsible.
OL,12,FAmong them is Gelvana, whose seven-
OL,13,Fyear-old son Thiago was overwhelmed in
OL,14,Fthe avalanche of mining waste - and
OL,15,Fkilled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
