OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"We lost everything because of greed."
OL,8,FGelvana told ITV News. Thiago was
OL,9,Ffound 100 kilometres from the village
OL,10,Fof Bento Rodrigues, where he had been
OL,11,Fwith his grandmother just before the
OL,12,Fdam collapsed.
OL,14,F"Justice in the UK courts would mean
OL,15,Feverything. It is the only thing that
OL,16,Fgives me hope," she added.
OL,18,FThe parent company of the dam's
OL,19,Foperators was BHP ` which is part
OL,20,FBritish-owned.
