OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FCompensation is expected to reach #36
OL,8,Fbillion, in what is already considered
OL,9,Fone of the world's largest collective
OL,10,Fenvironmental lawsuits.
OL,12,FThe case can be heard at the High
OL,13,FCourt because, at the time of the
OL,14,Fdisaster, BHP was listed on the London
OL,15,FStock Exchange ` and so this becomes
OL,16,Fthe appropriate jurisdiction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
