OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FTom Goodhead, who is representing all
OL,8,F620,000 claimants, said in a
OL,9,Fstatement: "The time has come for BHP
OL,10,Fto be confronted in court about its
OL,11,Finvolvement in the Mariana dam
OL,12,Fcollapse.
OL,14,F"We are committed to ensuring that the
OL,15,Fvictims finally receive due
OL,16,Fcompensation for the damage they have
OL,17,Fsuffered and thus set a precedent for
OL,18,Flarge corporations to be held
OL,19,Faccountable for their actions around
OL,20,Fthe world."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
