OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe case is due to last for 12 weeks
OL,8,Fand a ruling on who was liable for
OL,9,Fthis disaster is expected to come in
OL,10,FSummer 2025.
OL,12,FSo nothing is imminent, yet for those
OL,13,Fwho have travelled thousands of miles
OL,14,Ffrom Brazil to be here ` justice in
OL,15,Fthe English courts means everything.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
