OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FMarcelo Krenak, Chief of the
OL,8,FIndigenous Krenak community said:
OL,9,F"They came here and destroyed nature,
OL,10,Fdestroyed the trees, took away the
OL,11,Fnatural habitat of the animals, which
OL,12,Fhad nowhere to go and died. In a
OL,13,Fwhile, we won't be able to survive
OL,14,Feither, because the Rio Doce used to
OL,15,Fsustain our entire community.
OL,17,F"We want justice and we realise that,
OL,18,Fin Brazil, every time we speak out to
OL,19,Fdefend our rights, we are criminalised
OL,20,Fand penalised. We hope that it will be
OL,21,Fdifferent in England!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
