OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FBHP has referred to the dam collapse
OL,8,Fas "a tragedy," and in a statement
OL,9,Fahead of today's court case said its
OL,10,F"deepest sympathies remain with the
OL,11,Fimpacted families and communities".
OL,13,F"BHP Brasil is working collectively
OL,14,Fwith the Brazilian authorities and
OL,15,Fothers to seek solutions to finalise
OL,16,Ffull compensation and rehabilitation
OL,17,Fprocess that would keep funds in
OL,18,FBrazil for the Brazilian people and
OL,19,Fenvironment affected including
OL,20,Fimpacted traditional and indigenous
OL,21,Fcommunities.
