OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FJonathan Knowles, from Yorkshire, was
OL,8,Fforced to leave his home, wife and
OL,9,Fchild in Brazil after the Dam disaster.
OL,11,FHe told ITV News: "I haven't received
OL,12,Fa penny in compensation. In truth, I
OL,13,Fdon't think they really care. I lost
OL,14,Fmy family, was bankrupt, I had to come
OL,15,Fback to the UK and start again."
