OL,3,C'We lost everything': High court case
OL,4,Cfor Brazil's Mariana Dam disaster
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThis remains one of Brazil's worst-
OL,8,Fever environmental disasters. In the
OL,9,Fcoming months, the High Court shall
OL,10,Fdecide what part, if any a British
OL,11,Fcompany played in this human and
OL,12,Fecological catastrophe.
OL,14,FA BHP spokesperson told ITV News in a
OL,15,Fstatement: "The Fundao dam failure was
OL,16,Fa tragedy, and our deepest sympathies
OL,17,Fremain with the impacted families and
OL,18,Fcommunities.
