OL,7,F"BHP Brasil continues to work closely
OL,8,Fwith Samarco and Vale to support the
OL,9,Fongoing remediation and compensation
OL,10,Fprocess in Brazil.
OL,12,F"The Renova Foundation, established in
OL,13,F2016 (by Samarco, Vale and BHP Brasil)
OL,14,Fas part of the first agreement with
OL,15,Fthe Brazilian authorities, has spent
OL,16,Fmore than US$7.9 billion on emergency
OL,17,Ffinancial assistance, compensation and
OL,18,Frepair and rebuilding of environment
OL,19,Fand infrastructure to approximately
OL,20,F430,000 individuals, local businesses
OL,21,Fand indigenous communities.
